name: Year of the tiger 2022
description:
This token brings good luck, cleans karma, washes dishes, irons trousers and smoothes wrinkles, sometimes walks your pet and even less often cooks breakfast, unsubscribes from inactive people on Twitter and glows in the dark, but this is not accurate))

According to the lunar calendar, the Year of the Tiger begins on February 1st. I wish you good luck all year long!
